Network Commands

docker network ls-Lists available Docker networks.
docker network create mynetwork-Creates a custom network.
docker network inspect mynetwork-Shows network details.
docker network rm mynetwork-Deletes a network.

Cleanup Commands

docker stop $(docker ps -aq)-Stops all containers.
docker rm $(docker ps -aq)-Removes all containers.
docker rmi $(docker images -q)-Deletes all images.
docker system prune –a-Cleans unused containers, networks, images.


